## issue:41064358 bug6: 语句摘要函数 statement_digest()/statement_digest_text(),参数的SQL语句有换行，mysql与ob输出格式不一样。
select statement_digest('
SELECT CONCAT(last_name,", ",first_name) AS full_name
FROM mytable 
WHERE id > 10
ORDER BY full_name
limit 5;') digest from dual;
