## issue:41064358 bug6: 语句摘要函数 statement_digest()/statement_digest_text(),参数的SQL语句含有?，mysql失败，ob成功。
select statement_digest('SELECT * FROM tl WHERE id < ? ORDER BY c1 LIMIT ?') digest,statement_digest_text('SELECT * FROM tl WHERE id < ? ORDER BY c1 LIMIT ?') digest_text from dual;
